@startuml yaml_diff_workflow_context
skinparam defaultFontName "Noto Sans JP"
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ComponentBorderColor #555555
skinparam NoteBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7

rectangle "4フェーズワークフロー" {

  component "**Phase-0**\nyaml_diff.py\nYAML 差分検出" as P0 #AED6F1
  component "**Phase-A**\noutput_diff.py\nOutput 差分検出" as PA #A9DFBF
  component "**Phase-B**\ncause_classifier.py\n原因自動分類" as PB #F9E79F
  component "**Phase-C**\n手動レビュー /\n新マッチャー追加" as PC #F1948A

}

P0 -right-> PA : カバレッジ確認後\nPhase-A へ
PA -right-> PB : annotations.json
PB -right-> PC : cause_detail.csv\n(Unknown 行)
PC -up-> PA : C-3 完了後\nPhase-A 再実行

P0 -[dashed]down-> PC : 未カバー diff_type 発覚時\nC-3 先行実施

note bottom of P0
  before YAML が未入手の場合は
  Phase-0 をスキップして
  Phase-A へ直接進む
end note

note top of PA
  output_diff.py: OUTPUT フォルダ比較
  → annotations.json スケルトン生成
end note

@enduml
